pageContext.claim: “I had such a big lead in all of these states late into election night, only to see the leads miraculously disappear as the days went by. Perhaps these leads will return as our legal proceedings move forward!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump was leading in many states because not all the votes had been counted. In many places, the outstanding votes were from predominantly Democratic counties. There is no reason to believe that anything illegal happened as the remaining votes were counted.
